<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="tender-adj">tender <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'tendə(r)/    美 /'tendər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>和善的；温柔的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>tender words / looks
亲切的话语/表情</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>(食物) 嫩的；软的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 tough </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Cook for an hour or until the meat is tender.
煮一小时或煮到肉变软为止。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>纤弱的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>tender young plants
娇嫩的幼苗</p></div></div>